item.title: About Pranjal
item.description:
Hey there! I am Pranjal Aswani and I program computers for a living.

This blog was initially written as part of my participation in Google Summer of code in 2018, working with the wonderful CHAOSS community.

Now it will hopefully serve as my personal blog.

Like many developers, I have a keen interest in tech, music, books philosophy & sci-fi specifically.
